      "author": {
        "_account_id": 112,
        "name": "Oleg Drokin",
        "email": "green@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "green"
      },
      "date": "2013-02-04 21:47:35.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7: (4 inline comments)\n\nI suspect having per ost amd mdt module pingless option might be best (or perhaps even per-filesystem for extra flexibility where some of the filesystems don't have the infrastructure and some do - fine as a separate patch).\n\nThat would also have a side benefit of mgs not having the option and thus always requiring pings (for now, at least).",
